            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E7%96%BC%E8%BF%98%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E8%A6%81%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E7%96%BC%E8%BF%98%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E8%A6%81%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不疼还增大的乳腺结节要当心#</span></a>！】目前，乳腺癌已成全球第一大癌症。乳腺结节包括乳腺癌，也包括乳腺的增生结节、乳腺囊肿及乳腺纤维瘤等良性肿瘤，绝大部分乳腺结节都是良性的。医生介绍，若结节没有疼痛且不断增大，要严格重视。如果检查提示乳腺结节有恶性风险，要尽快处理。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>  <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4865360785244210" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1har83jduu8j60rk0fiakf02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Yo2rxHOplx082SzADivS01041200j11X0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675717639&amp;ssig=tpTRj5bxQY&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/eA7wWO6Dlx082SzAkGas010412009APw0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675717639&amp;ssig=QmudIlJ91V&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/F2oyb9uXlx082SzA39cs0104120068mG0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675717639&amp;ssig=nES0nKVxGl&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4865360785244210&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
